一.各种灯光建筑的效果图：
    1.在温和地形，原始环境照明为1.0时
第一行：Invisible Green Light Post；Invisible Red Light Post；Invisible Blue Light Post
第二行：Invisible Light Post；Invisible Yellow Light Post
第三行：Invisible Purple Light Post；Negative Light Post
第一行：InvisibleTemperateMorningLamp；InvisibleTemperateDayLamp；InvisibleTemperateDuskLamp
第二行：InvisibleTemperateNightLamp；InvisibleSnowMorningLamp
第三行：InvisibleSnowDayLamp；InvisibleSnowDuskPost；InvisibleSnowNightLamp
    2.在雪地地形，原始环境照明为0.8时
第一行：Invisible Green Light Post__Invisible Red Light Post__Invisible Blue Light Post__Invisible Light Post
第二行：Invisible Yellow Light Post__Invisible Purple Light Post__Negative Light Post
第三行：InvisibleTemperateMorningLamp__InvisibleTemperateDayLamp__InvisibleTemperateDuskLamp__InvisibleTemperateNightLamp
第四行：InvisibleSnowMorningLamp__InvisibleSnowDayLamp__InvisibleSnowDuskPost__InvisibleSnowNightLamp
